  "title": "Retail Assistant [Takashimaya Cake & Cupcake Store] (ML06)",
  "description": "<p>Position: <strong>Part-time Retail Assistant</strong></p><p>Location: Takashimaya</p><p>Working days: 4 days per week</p><p>Working hours: Schedule based on roster</p><p>Salary: $11 per hour</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>Assist with daily store operations and upkeep</p><p>Take customer orders accurately and provide excellent service</p><p>Handle cashiering and payment transactions</p><p>Ensure cleanliness and hygiene standards are maintained</p><p><br /></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>Must possess a valid Food Safety and Hygiene Certificate</p><p>Able to start work immediately</p><p>Able to commit at least 3 to 4 days per week</p><p>Short shifts (2–4 hours) are acceptable</p><p>Must be able to work on weekends and public holidays</p><p>Willing to work according to rostered schedule</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>📩 Welcome to apply through WhatsApp, Please send me your resume.</p><p>📱WhatsApp: ‪‪‪‪‪+65 8928 7217‬‬‬‬ (‬Contact person：Mandy Lu）</p><p>🔗 ‪‪‪‪https://wa.me/6589287217‬</p><p><br /></p>",
